reviews.text:
Went to the Wednesday night quiz. It was a lot of fun and quite busy with everyone inside and a few people outside participating.

I had a non alcoholic cocktail which was really interesting and different. Wonderful flavours.
This is a lovely cafe with amazing coffee and nibbles. Charming like the ones in Melbourne, and nice staffs. So glad that we went there on our last day in HK!
Great AllPress coffee. Small cute cafe for a quick stop. Iced choc for kids. Only plan to stop for 15-20 as it’s small and busy. Still worth it for the coffee!

Winstons Coffee is 1 of the best in my wishlist when it comes having a coffee for refreshments. They got skillful baristas that can make perfect shots every single time, recommended especially for visitors

Being a big fan of Allpress in London, I was delighted to stumble upon Winstons in HK. Every bit as good as the London coffee chain. Not sure if it’s the same owners. Wouldn’t be surprised as the food was a similar format. An awesome daily ritual during my time there

reviews.text: 가게는 좁지만 역바로 옆 길가에 확트여있어 분위기가좋다. 항상 사람이 많음. 커피는 향이 좋고 맛도 좋다. 서비스로 주는 빵도 너무 맛있고. 주문한 크로와상도 맛있었음. 커피와 베이커리 모두 만족. 샌드위치도 많이들 먹는것 같은데 도전해볼만하다.

Went to the Wednesday night quiz. It was a lot of fun and quite busy with everyone inside and a few people outside participating.

I had a non alcoholic cocktail which was really interesting and different. Wonderful flavours.
This is a lovely cafe with amazing coffee and nibbles. Charming like the ones in Melbourne, and nice staffs. So glad that we went there on our last day in HK!
호텔근처에서 맛있는 커피집 발견. 크지 않은 실내의 작은 커피가게이지만 맛은 최고 입니다. 몇가지 종류의 샌드워치도 팔지만 앉아서 먹을 자리가 없어서 커피만 주문하고 옆 공원의 벤치에 앉아 여유를 즐기다 갑니다.
